                <p>
                    We strive to provide a reliable Service but do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We may modify, suspend, or discontinue parts of the Service at any time, with or without notice.
                </p>

                <h2>10. Termination</h2>
                <p>You may stop using the Service at any time.</p>
                <p>We may suspend or terminate your access if:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>You violate these Terms</li>
                    <li>Payment obligations are not met</li>
                    <li>Continued use poses legal, security, or operational risk</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
